{"tid":2065166,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"70歲日本啃老族 一生只打過兩年工 成世人都靠父母遺產過活","createTime":"2020-06-15T11:00:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T11:55:07.000Z","uid":312363,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f236c7adebfbe6d766707302597e568fd05934be","tid":2065166,"uid":312363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T11:00:30.000Z","msg":"前田良久爺爺，人生中只有求職過一次，工作了兩年。<br />\n<br />\n兩年後父母過世，就決定辭職回家，住著父母在東京豪宅區留下的房屋，靠著父母的大筆遺產過一輩子。<br />\n<br />\n由於前田一生只工作過短短的兩年，所以即使年過退休之齡都沒有退休金。<br />\n<br />\n他從來沒有談過戀愛，生活亦不追求大富大費，樸簡地獨自生活到70歲。<br />\n<br />\n儘管一大筆 遺產也有用盡的一天，所以他生活非常節儉，每個月的花費大概都控制在6萬日幣以內(約4,000港元)。<br />\n<br />\n前田家中雪櫃只有納豆，而衣櫃則塞滿洋蔥。<br />\n<br />\n三餐只吃納豆補充蛋白質，偶爾才有飯配洋蔥，吃完飯後就把餐具放回櫃子裡，因為懶惰而不洗碗筷，而食物包裝就隨地亂扔。<br />\n<br />\n他每天唯一活動就是外出散步，然後繼續無所事事地度過一天。<br />\n<br />\n他每天都當作最後一天地生活，所以家裡都亂七八糟，雜物、垃圾堆滿整間屋子，根本看不見地板。<br />\n<br />\n來採訪的日本電視台替他打掃家中，竟清理出1噸的垃圾。<br />\n<br />\n前田本來還有一個妹妹，但前幾年也不幸過世，家族只剩下他一個人。<br />\n<br />\n雖然前田說偶爾會人感到孤單，但也滿意這樣的生活，估算父母的遺產大約還夠他花7至8年。<br />\n<br />\n他表示當遺產用完的那一天，就會決定離開這個世界。<br />\n<br />\n「反正一個人孤零零，也沒有什麼目標或夢想，沒有值得留戀的地方。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WwMgNf6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWwMgNf6.jpg&h=eb740f3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gGcDf9w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgGcDf9w.jpg&h=bdf34860&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SwpY0Bk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSwpY0Bk.jpg&h=fbfc5743&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mGSLFBo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmGSLFBo.jpg&h=53db31fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dsNGYnV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdsNGYnV.jpg&h=a339c1d7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"86004b216d28553863ce03a8e62c4f35279b944d","tid":2065166,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T11:01:25.000Z","msg":"可憐可憐"},{"pid":"d0368acdd1cdc91a76d70258f36fc2981c34e15a","tid":2065166,"uid":11962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T11:01:57.000Z","msg":"有錢但可悲"},{"pid":"3d0300c0ccf97b1d1e10f9809ca7e1aaedd25200","tid":2065166,"uid":100772,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T11:04:32.000Z","msg":"佢都話成日飲酒<br />\n日日叫雞賭錢冇講出黎 不知幾爽"},{"pid":"793609389e276329baa9b3a1c2de3629c3f140e0","tid":2065166,"uid":243380,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d0368acdd1cdc91a76d70258f36fc2981c34e15a","tid":2065166,"uid":11962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T11:01:57.000Z","msg":"有錢但可悲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T11:05:10.000Z","msg":"4000*8*12=38萬港紙<br />\n同有錢差好遠喎.."},{"pid":"dbe14177f306d4164baf586708a10ebe898ffe8d","tid":2065166,"uid":39383,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T11:07:52.000Z","msg":"佢自己都鐘意過咁既生活就無咩問題啦, 我都羨慕了<br />\n但兩老乜柒都無, 啃返我轉頭就有<br />\n<br />\nbtw, 啃返自己個仔, 呢d 叫咩族?"},{"pid":"f56334a5bbdfd3ea52700b16c9fc533589171d89","tid":2065166,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T11:10:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.cup.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/6000598447554560-400x280.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cup.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F05%2F6000598447554560-400x280.jpg&h=7e9a187e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"df76b08001f035ffa4ab305e078e3c764aa3b6a7","tid":2065166,"uid":106633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T11:12:00.000Z","msg":"阿伯就覺得生存就係生存最大既意義<br />\n其他學術工作財富感情上種種既成就都冇意義<br />\n只係被生落嚟就繼續活下去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a010f2b687dc14bf1b6972259a3246afa9538a24","tid":2065166,"uid":342115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"793609389e276329baa9b3a1c2de3629c3f140e0","tid":2065166,"uid":243380,"lik